{"tid":1048017,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港遠古本土文化　拜石狗　","createTime":"2019-03-05T10:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T12:51:33.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ceb32843c0bc572b5a3866aff63dc94d15bfdef1","tid":1048017,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:52:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/culture/system/2019/02/21/010110493.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fculture%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F02%2F21%2F010110493.shtml&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXrhFCD9B5Ks%2BF8NlIfSW%2BYc%3D&h=4d7f0d05\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/culture/system/2019/02/21/010110493.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n香港早期的原住民保留了山歌、茶果、盆菜、二次葬、拜石狗等習俗。<br />\n<br />\n大嶼山大澳吉慶後街路旁，有一土地神壇，壇內供奉一石狗，及兩三尖形石塊，上為拱形鐵皮遮蓋。據考證，石狗為畬傜之圖騰，廣東及廣西土著多有祀奉。石狗之祀，以其能驅邪治魔，為民間之守護神，所以多放置在路邊巷頭，以守山坡、江河、水口、墳地及宗祠。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/19/35/10193521_029281.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F19%2F35%2F10193521_029281.jpg&h=27568c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大澳石狗 圖：香港歷史遊蹤"},{"pid":"231f3f948dd6a3dd14a83b1e87a8fcd6539547ca","tid":1048017,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02b5e67690ff05ae780082f3bab1beb2337fa31","tid":1048017,"uid":67574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:54:07.000Z","msg":"蕭國健<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a607bf0575781b3eaff4ccee941e19422461ff","tid":1048017,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T11:04:00.000Z","msg":"融合文化就係香港文化！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27eab630435904b753566d8e8b7eff771eae9641","tid":1048017,"uid":25643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"qu